<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Mis 15 Años - DANNA CAMILA</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins&family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  background: black;
}

/* PORTADA */
<section class="hero">
  <div class="overlay"></div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <h2 class="brush">Mis 15 Años</h2>

    <h1 class="paint">
      DANNA CAMILA
    </h1>

    <p class="sub">BARRERA AVILA</p>
  </div>
</section> 

.overlay {
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
}

.hero {
  height: 100vh;
  background: url('https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/ea/The_Starry_Night.JPG') no-repeat center/cover;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  position: relative;
}

.overlay {
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
}

.hero-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  text-align: center;
  color: white;
}

/* TEXTO PINCEL */
.brush {
  font-size: 3em;
  color: gold;
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
}

/* EFECTO ESCRITURA (PINCEL) */
.paint {
  font-size: 3em;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  white-space: nowrap;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-right: 3px solid gold;
  width: 0;
  margin: auto;
  animation: escribir 4s steps(30) forwards, parpadeo 0.7s infinite;
}

/* SUBTEXTO */
.sub {
  letter-spacing: 5px;
  margin-top: 10px;
}

/* ANIMACIONES */
@keyframes escribir {
  from { width: 0 }
  to { width: 100% }
}

@keyframes parpadeo {
  50% { border-color: transparent }
} 
@keyframes zoomBg {
  from { transform: scale(1); }
  to { transform: scale(1.1); }
} 

.brush-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 3.5em;
  color: #facc15;
  text-shadow:
    2px 2px 0 #000,
    4px 4px 10px rgba(255,215,0,0.8),
    0 0 25px rgba(255,215,0,0.6);
  animation: paint 2s ease;
}

@keyframes paint {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: scale(0.8) rotate(-5deg);
  }
  to {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(1) rotate(0);
  }
} 

.big15 {
  font-size: 2em;
  text-shadow: 0 0 15px gold;
}

.main-name {
  font-size: 3em;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
}

.sub-name {
  letter-spacing: 5px;
}

/* TARJETA */
.card {
  padding: 40px 20px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #020617, #000);
}

/* BOTÓN */
.btn {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 20px;
  padding: 12px 25px;
  background: gold;
  color: black;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 25px;
}

/* CONTADOR */
.countdown {
  font-size: 1.5em;
  margin-top: 20px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- PORTADA -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h2 class="brush-title">Mis <span class="big15">15</span> Años</h2>
    <h1 class="main-name">DANNA CAMILA</h1>
    <p class="sub-name">BARRERA AVILA</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CONTENIDO -->
<div class="card">

<p>📅 1 de agosto de 2026</p>
<p>🕖 7:00 PM</p>

<p style="margin-top:15px;">
Bajo una noche llena de estrellas, queremos celebrar esta fecha tan especial contigo.<br><br>
Tenemos el honor de invitarte a la celebración de los 15 años de<br>
<strong>DANNA CAMILA BARRERA AVILA</strong>
</p>

<p>
👗 Dress Code:<br>
Formal elegante (damas y caballeros)<br>
🚫 Evitar color azul oscuro
</p>

<p style="margin-top:20px; font-style:italic;">
✨ Tu presencia hará esta noche aún más especial ✨
</p>

<div class="countdown" id="countdown"></div>

<a class="btn" href="https://wa.me/573223371728">Confirmar asistencia</a>

<br><br>

<button class="btn" onclick="playMusic()">🎵 Activar música</button>

<audio id="music" loop>
  <source src="https://www.bensound.com/bensound-music/bensound-slowmotion.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
</audio>

</div>

<script>
var countDownDate = new Date("Aug 1, 2026 19:00:00").getTime();

var x = setInterval(function() {
  var now = new Date().getTime();
  var distance = countDownDate - now;

  var days = Math.floor(distance / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24));
  var hours = Math.floor((distance % (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)) / (1000 * 60 * 60));
  var minutes = Math.floor((distance % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60));
  var seconds = Math.floor((distance % (1000 * 60)) / 1000);

  document.getElementById("countdown").innerHTML =
  days + " días " + hours + "h " + minutes + "m " + seconds + "s ";

}, 1000);

function playMusic() {
  document.getElementById("music").play();
}
</script>

</body>
</html> 
